tion><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/DQiJdiW.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>If you know, you know.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/j3PZwfp</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Resistance1000]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>The kind of thing you will never need and you will never achieve if you will ever need it.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/TnUcl2W</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/3QxtvXe.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/TnUcl2W</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[kenistod]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Monday morning down the Hormuz…</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/uqXq0Si</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/fZf6R5q.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/uqXq0Si</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Litherger]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Fuck it, here’s a song I’m working on</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/abpBGpv</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Iv7NqLe.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>FRONT PAGE EDIT: 

Cannot thank you all enough for the kind words and encouragement. I've been at such a low I really needed the boost. I want to keep sharing with all y'all who would want to keep up, so if you wanna give me a follow or go to my linktree and find me elsewhere, please do. I'm excited to use a couple of my own works as assignments/practice for my last quarter at school (audio engineering), and I'm excited to share the results.

To the person who said Imgur is not like Tiktok or Insta, holy hell you were correct. I meant it in the way of "I'm posting to no one here, so may as well post to no one there," just to realize OH I am not posting to no one. It's so refreshing to know there's a pocket online where the community means something, without the need for paid advertisements or where algorithms are working against you. This is the first time I felt like I shared to a real group of people.

I'm definitely going to go to open mics around town, even if I don't have the guts to perform again yet, but I think some folks were right about needing to go out in the real world because the community surely is there. Just scary for me (chronic dissociation issues, socialization is hard). 

I want to post regularly here, but I don't want to be annoying, so maybe I'll leave it to once a week or something, idk, I'll figure it out. Bear with me as my stuff gets kinda weird, but it's honest to me and it's who I am as an artist. 

THANK YOU again for the support. 
I feel a little more real today <3. 

www.linktr.ee/innerwilds

Original Post
----------
Yesterday I made a big long post about my feelings, about dissociation, and the pain of sharing music to no one versus the pain of keeping it all in. If you’re interested in that, go give it a read.

A few people said “share” so what the hell. 
It’s no different posting it here than on TikTok or Insta or YouTube.

I wrote this one a couple of days ago because I’ve been stuck in this mentally unwell cycle for years, I know it’s no one else’s job to fix me, but I really don’t know how to move forward on my own either. I just keep thinking I’ll figure it out someday.

It’s not at full release yet, but I intend to share a stripped and full version.

ALSO ITS BODY PAINT
I just like putting body paint on. 
Honestly it’s been kind of a strange but useful anti-self harm tactic.

Take care of yourselves out there. None of this shit is easy.

Artist name is Inner Wilds.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/abpBGpv</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[ThrockTheGrass]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Be best, JD!</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/Mi9xxde</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Iteq3kn.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/Mi9xxde</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[LollipopsCorner]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>That’s how you do it baby!!!</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/vgu1IvY</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/NoxkJnC.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/vgu1IvY</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[malbec]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Can we get a Bald Ackles Supernatural sitcom?</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/VahmSIr</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/viMJbwI.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Cas can be the next door neighbor</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/VahmSIr</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Headcase444]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Not sure this is the right meme, but it works</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/hTIOruW</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/EYdB5Q5.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Saw someone say this and needed to make it a graphic. This was the best I could come up with</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/hTIOruW</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[LadyCritCat]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Elect clowns, get a circus</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/qKAUQqp</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/NbUVklZ.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></d